{"tid":731580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獵人盜獵犀牛反遭獅群斷頭分屍　遺骸僅剩一顆頭顱","createTime":"2018-07-06T09:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T11:32:32.000Z","uid":75969,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"604d42d600dadb01db35134080cc06e0cf34498a","tid":731580,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:48:11.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n螳螂捕蟬，黃雀在後！南非西布亞野生動物保育區（Sibuya Game Reserve）日前有一群獵人偷闖進來想盜獵犀牛角，沒想到遇上獅群，當場被斷頭分食，現場留有人體殘肢。不過當地管理員表示，因為遺骸所剩不多，沒辦法確定有多少人被殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/07/06/1432882-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F1432882-XXL.jpg&h=963dcd83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲獅子將盜獵者分屍。（示意圖／翻攝自臉書Kruger National Park）</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，保護區巡邏員在南非西布亞（Sibuya）區域<span style=\"color: red;\">找到人類遺骸，旁邊還有步槍、斧頭、消音器</span>，而這些物品被認為是盜獵犀牛的工具，同時還在附近找到3雙鞋，但無法確定盜獵者究竟有多少，因為遺骸數量相當稀少，僅有一顆頭顱跟一個骨盆。<br />\n<br />\n保護區管理員尼克福斯（Nick Fox）說，「盜獵者不小心晃入獅群中，而這獅群相當大，因此他們沒有太多時間逃跑。」同時也表示，沒必要繼續深入搜索，因為不清楚那群獅子把獵物帶到哪裡。<br />\n<br />\n由於不少人認為犀牛角能夠壯陽、保健身體，以致犀牛盜獵的狀況日益嚴重。尼克福斯說，他們曾在一個月內失去3頭犀牛，對於這回是獅子先遇上獵人，而非獵人先找到犀牛，他感到慶幸，「獅子是我們最好的警衛，你們（盜獵者）不可能是永遠的贏家！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=400636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D400636&d=tIRv%2FMGLmht8M4%2Fqae7Cx9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8d7e6b10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D400636&h=42f3b7f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=400636</a><br />\n<br />\n有步槍都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da3a33078bbe2e709e5f6a6eefe81ba09eadf94","tid":731580,"uid":136770,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"73a297d12786374b2df3d661667042f82da2b5e7","tid":731580,"uid":161731,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:49:15.000Z","msg":"好波牙C"},{"pid":"118e2a3a3c7af8c447e4a2ae100637343ae13665","tid":731580,"uid":61954,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:49:54.000Z","msg":"佢係一個好獵人"},{"pid":"62e56ce95e6d0717e92a4a9ff73c62179556363f","tid":731580,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"我估係夜間捕獵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23687df0d6bb9e055b078d6fb8d09a615c41419f","tid":731580,"uid":146604,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"獅子：嘩 有朱古力食啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075248837f73d1653b26e22d54360c639733ea39","tid":731580,"uid":20241,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:56:34.000Z","msg":"保護區管理員尼克福斯（Nick Fox）說，WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<del>「盜獵者不小心晃入獅群中，而這獅群相當大，因此他們沒有太多時間逃跑。」同時也表示，沒必要繼續深入搜索，因為不清楚那群獅子把獵物帶到哪裡。</del>"},{"pid":"694f6c6feec0cf4b5a951aee4fcee1ff0d1fe2bf","tid":731580,"uid":7840,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2c1db6b0217d08482de625ba9c5dd91c0545cad","tid":731580,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"連頭骨都食撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfd86804e4d1f3bcfc0618dfef158d0beb754d9","tid":731580,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c1db6b0217d08482de625ba9c5dd91c0545cad","tid":731580,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"連頭骨都食撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:13:44.000Z","msg":"人骨相對柔軟，食埋骨髓更飽肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm